== Introduction to commands
	Eclipse IDE extensions use the commands framework to
		contribute
		actions to the user interface. This concept is based on
		extension
		points.
	
	
		This description explains the usage of commands in Eclipse IDE
		extensions. To define and use a command you have to define three
		extensions.
		The following extension points are relevant to define a
		menu
		or toolbar
		contribution for an Eclipse plug-in.

